T1  - How Do Peer Awards Motivate Creative Content? Experimental Evidence from Reddit
AU  - Burtch, Gordon
AU  - He, Qinglai
AU  - Hong, Yili
AU  - Lee, Dokyun
Y1  - 2021/06/01
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2022/05/01
