T1  - Changes in Risky Benefits and in Risky Costs: A Question of the Right Order
AU  - Menegatti, Mario
AU  - Peter, Richard
Y1  - 2021/08/20
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2022/05/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2021.4081
